---

## File Structure

```
index.html        ← Entire dashboard (single self-contained file)
README.md         ← This file
```

No frameworks, no build tools, no npm. Just open `index.html` in a browser or push to GitHub Pages.

---

## Updating the Dashboard

1. Export a labor report from PMWare for the desired date range
2. Open `index.html` in a text editor
3. Search for the data section you want to update (KPI stats, Top 10 tables, shift hours, ticker items)
4. Update the values
5. Commit and push — GitHub Pages will reflect the changes within a minute or two

> **Tip:** After pushing, do a hard refresh in your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R / Cmd+Shift+R) to clear the cache and see the latest version.

